sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User as BI Developer
    participant FE as Angular Frontend
    participant API as Flask API
    participant TP as TMDL Parser
    participant BA as BPA Analyzer
    participant IA as Inspector Analyzer
    participant PA as Page Analyzer
    participant TE as Tabular Editor CLI
    participant PI as PBI Inspector CLI
    participant PG as PostgreSQL
    participant MG as MongoDB

    User->>FE: Create Project
    FE->>API: POST /api/projects
    API->>PG: INSERT Project
    PG-->>API: Project created
    API-->>FE: Project {id, name, status: pending}

    User->>FE: Upload PBIP ZIP
    FE->>API: POST /api/projects/{id}/upload
    API->>API: Extract ZIP to /uploads/{id}/
    API->>API: Validate PBIP structure
    API-->>FE: Upload success

    User->>FE: Click Analyze
    FE->>API: POST /api/projects/{id}/analyze
    API->>PG: SET status = analyzing

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over API,MG: Step 1: TMDL Parsing
        API->>TP: parse_full_model(definition_dir)
        TP->>TP: Parse tables, columns, measures
        TP->>TP: Parse relationships, roles
        TP->>TP: Extract data sources from M queries
        TP-->>API: Catalog JSON
        API->>PG: INSERT ModelTable, ModelColumn, ModelMeasure...
        API->>MG: INSERT raw model_catalog
    end

    rect rgb(255, 243, 224)
        Note over API,TE: Step 2: BPA Analysis
        API->>BA: run_bpa(definition_dir)
        BA->>TE: Execute TabularEditor.exe -A rules.json -V
        TE-->>BA: Console output with violations
        BA->>BA: Parse violations, match fix templates
        BA-->>API: Violations JSON
        API->>PG: INSERT BpaViolation, BpaSummary
        API->>MG: INSERT raw bpa_results
    end

    rect rgb(232, 245, 233)
        Note over API,PI: Step 3: PBI Inspector
        API->>IA: run_inspector(report_dir)
        IA->>PI: Execute PBIRInspectorCLI.exe
        PI-->>IA: TestRun_*.json
        IA->>IA: Parse inspector results
        IA-->>API: Results JSON
        API->>PG: INSERT InspectorResult
        API->>MG: INSERT raw inspector_results
    end

    rect rgb(243, 229, 245)
        Note over API,MG: Step 4: Page Layout Extraction
        API->>PA: analyze_pages(report_dir)
        PA->>PA: Walk pages/*/page.json
        PA->>PA: Extract visuals/*/visual.json
        PA-->>API: Page layouts JSON
        API->>MG: INSERT raw page_layouts
    end

    API->>PG: SET status = ready, UPDATE counts
    API->>API: Cleanup uploaded files
    API-->>FE: Analysis complete
    FE-->>User: Dashboard ready
